This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and
retain certain data when you use our online service.

Information We Collect

We retain server logs of API requests.

The information we collect includes
information submitted on your behalf by ChatGPT (namely, the link to an AI
generated image and inscription text), as well as certain information appended
to that request by OpenAI.
